1. Project Description
Hello, my name is Monopolyon. I present to you an interesting
and exciting Project. This is an interactive entertainment board.
One of the main ideas of this board is the dynamic change in the
areas located on it. The areas change their sizes depending on the
sizes of the browser window or monitor if the browser is expanded
to full screen, while their percentage ratios always remain the
same. Let's consider a few simple examples:"
Suppose that on our board there are three sections with a total
amount of 600 MNP. Jack has 300 MNP, another 150 MNP belongs
to Harry and 150 MNP to Mary. On the board, this will look as
follows."
Jack - 300 MNP - 50%
Harry- 150 MNP -25%
Mary - 150 MNP - 25%
"
"
"
If everyone owned the same amount of MNP then the board
would look like this:"
"
"
Jack - 200 MNP - 33%
Harry - 200 MNP -33%
Mary - 200 MNP - 33%
The algorithm automatically distributes sections in accordance
with the amount of MNP"
A few more examples:
In this example, we will have 4 sections:"
"
Jack - 1000 MNP - 50%
Harry - 400 MNP - 20%
Mary - 400 MNP - 20%
Anna - 200 MNP - 10%
"
"
And again, if everyone has an equal amount, then the board will
look like this:"
"
Jack - 500 MNP - 25%
Harry - 500 MNP - 25%
Mary - 500 MNP - 25%
Anna - 500 MNP - 25%
"
A large number of sections can t on the board."
